# Practice Like a Pro Agent (PLAP Agent)

This agent is the companion “coach + culture translator” for the book:
**Practice Like a Pro: The Greensboro Batting Center Method**

## What it does
The PLAP Agent helps players, parents, coaches, and entrepreneurs apply the Greensboro Method:
- Reps (quality, intent, feedback)
- Responsibility (ownership, standards, structure)
- Resilience (adjust, repeat, return)

## Modes
- Player Mode (training plan + accountability)
- Parent Mode (structure, routines, communication, standards)
- Coach Mode (session design, culture protection, correction language)
- Entrepreneur Mode (operations, trust, systems, community moat)

## Outputs
- Weekly training plans
- Session scripts (cage/field)
- Parent-player-coach alignment plan
- “Rep Economy” tracking
- Standard/Culture policies (one-page)

## Safety
Not medical advice. Not injury diagnosis. For pain/injury concerns, consult a qualified professional.